her out than its\nboxy bulge, i.e. that the boxy bulge is only part of the bar, thus confirming\npredictions from orbital structure studies and from previous N-body\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2006 13:23:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 May 2006 09:57:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
